1
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:12,040
Your wedding is coming up,

2
00:00:12,200 --> 00:00:14,040
so I've ordered some wine for you.

3
00:00:14,399 --> 00:00:15,880
It's your favorite.

4
00:00:16,079 --> 00:00:18,680
I'll have Xiaoxue go check it out.

5
00:00:25,599 --> 00:00:27,040
I'll go help you with your nails.

6
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:30,759
No need.

7
00:00:31,519 --> 00:00:32,439
She's always done it,

8
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:33,839
and I'm used to it.

9
00:00:35,640 --> 00:00:37,920
Uncle, I'll go check it out.

10
00:00:38,240 --> 00:00:39,960
I don't trust anyone else

11
00:00:39,960 --> 00:00:40,920
with my wedding.

12
00:00:45,600 --> 00:00:47,640
Qingyou, I'm free later.

13
00:00:47,920 --> 00:00:48,720
I'll go with you.

14
00:00:49,799 --> 00:00:50,519
Okay.

15
00:00:56,079 --> 00:00:57,720
Let me take you for a facial.

16
00:00:58,640 --> 00:00:59,640
I don't want a facial.

17
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:03,000
Then I'll tidy up a bit.

18
00:01:04,039 --> 00:01:05,000
What's wrong with you?

19
00:01:05,360 --> 00:01:06,120
Nothing.

20
00:01:08,959 --> 00:01:10,200
Then why are you avoiding me?

21
00:01:10,959 --> 00:01:11,599
I'm not.

22
00:01:11,599 --> 00:01:13,400
Is it because of what I said?

23
00:01:14,360 --> 00:01:15,599
If I don't marry her,

24
00:01:16,519 --> 00:01:17,720
will you be with me?

25
00:01:18,599 --> 00:01:19,239
No.

26
00:01:20,519 --> 00:01:21,480
Then answer me.

27
00:01:23,679 --> 00:01:26,000
Young Master Yan, I can't answer you.

28
00:01:27,439 --> 00:01:28,640
I'm just a nurse,

29
00:01:28,879 --> 00:01:30,679
to put it bluntly, a maid.

30
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:33,360
What qualifications do I have to talk about this?

31
00:01:34,239 --> 00:01:35,519
You just need to answer me.

32
00:01:35,799 --> 00:01:37,319
I'll handle the rest.

33
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:41,560
I know you're the eldest young master of the Gu family.

34
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:43,599
You're the future successor of the Gu Group.

35
00:01:43,599 --> 00:01:45,319
You can solve anything.

36
00:01:45,599 --> 00:01:47,640
But I don't want to get involved in your world.

37
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:49,879
I'm nobody.

38
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,319
I can't handle it.

39
00:01:53,039 --> 00:01:54,439
You don't have to handle it.

40
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:07,359
Who gave you this?

41
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,840
This is the card Mr. Gu gave me a few days ago.

42
00:02:12,159 --> 00:02:13,879
He let me spend the money in it freely.

43
00:02:14,039 --> 00:02:15,520
But I don't want it.

44
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:17,479
But if I don't, he'll kick me out.

45
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,919
I don't know what to do.

46
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:23,879
Don't worry about him.

47
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,800
You can ignore him.

48
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,879
Mr Jing told me to ignore him too,

49
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,400
but I can't.

50
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,359
I'm nobody,

51
00:02:30,359 --> 00:02:31,560
just a servant.

52
00:02:36,319 --> 00:02:37,199
Don't say that.

53
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,560
Since the day

54
00:02:38,879 --> 00:02:39,960
you gave the ring I gave you

55
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:41,080
to Xia Wanqing,

56
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,400
I knew it was hard for you.

57
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:45,680
But

58
00:02:46,199 --> 00:02:47,199
I didn't

59
00:02:47,199 --> 00:02:48,599
just say that.

60
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:50,919
Help me pack up

61
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:52,960
and go try on the dress with me.

62
00:02:56,319 --> 00:02:58,039
Mr. Gu, the suit is here.

63
00:02:58,520 --> 00:02:59,400
Go try it on.

64
00:03:01,439 --> 00:03:02,359
Let her try on a suit, too.

65
00:03:03,199 --> 00:03:04,840
Why should I try on a suit?

66
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:07,479
How else will I know if it matches?

67
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:11,039
Xiao Han, help her change clothes.

68
00:03:11,039 --> 00:03:11,680
Okay.

69
00:03:12,039 --> 00:03:12,720
Let's go, Mr. Gu.

70
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,159
This way, please.

71
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:24,800
Wanqing.

72
00:03:25,039 --> 00:03:26,439
I have a party with my classmates this evening.

73
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:27,840
Do you have time?

74
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:32,879
Brother,

75
00:03:33,599 --> 00:03:34,680
I'm busy.

76
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,720
When did your leg get better?

77
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:41,760
It's been healed for a while.

78
00:04:42,479 --> 00:04:43,720
I wanted to give you a surprise.

79
00:04:47,599 --> 00:04:48,479
You know,

80
00:04:49,359 --> 00:04:51,119
I don't want to marry Xia Wanqing.

81
00:04:52,679 --> 00:04:53,999
I want to be with you.

82
00:05:03,039 --> 00:05:04,999
After I've sorted out the company,

83
00:05:05,999 --> 00:05:07,080
I'll come back and marry you.

84
00:05:08,919 --> 00:05:10,080
Will you wait for me?

85
00:05:38,799 --> 00:05:40,760
You only brought a few friends with you.

86
00:05:42,039 --> 00:05:43,640
You didn't bring your brother either.

87
00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:45,640
He's a stubborn old man.

88
00:05:45,999 --> 00:05:46,679
He wouldn't come.

89
00:05:48,919 --> 00:05:49,679
That's true.

90
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:25,320
Chengyan is back.

91
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:27,599
Bro, your leg...

92
00:07:28,400 --> 00:07:29,119
Bro,

93
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:31,359
when did your leg get better?

94
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:35,520
Just a couple of days ago.

95
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:38,119
Why didn't you tell me sooner?

96
00:07:38,799 --> 00:07:40,280
He wanted to give you a surprise.

97
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:43,559
Cheng Yan, your leg is healed just in time.

98
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:44,559
On the wedding day,

99
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:46,440
you can hold her hand

100
00:07:46,559 --> 00:07:48,280
and walk into the marriage hall together.

101
00:07:54,359 --> 00:07:55,840
This is all thanks to Xiaoxue.

102
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:57,919
Now my leg is healed,

103
00:07:58,599 --> 00:07:59,520
so I've decided

104
00:08:00,239 --> 00:08:02,359
Xiaoxue will no longer be my personal caregiver,

105
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:10,119
but my personal assistant.

106
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,720
Look, Yan Shaoye's leg is healed.

107
00:09:10,040 --> 00:09:10,680
Yeah.

108
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,840
Who's that girl next to him?

109
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:13,560
No idea.

110
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:19,519
Everyone's been working hard lately.

111
00:09:19,879 --> 00:09:20,879
Now that I'm back,

112
00:09:21,239 --> 00:09:23,200
I'll take over all company affairs.

113
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,519
The main issue

114
00:09:25,599 --> 00:09:26,759
is to urgently resolve

115
00:09:26,759 --> 00:09:28,599
the Su family acquisition case.

116
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:29,999
So,

117
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:32,519
my wedding with Miss Xia Wanqing

118
00:09:33,119 --> 00:09:34,080
will be kept simple,

119
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,119
mainly to entertain important clients.

120
00:09:36,399 --> 00:09:37,359
Any questions?

121
00:09:38,879 --> 00:09:39,960
I have no objections.

122
00:09:40,519 --> 00:09:41,840
Regarding the company and the wedding,

123
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,160
we'll follow Mr. Gu's lead.

124
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:45,479
Good.

125
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:49,040
Now, I'll announce a personnel change.

126
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:51,800
From now on, Ji Xiaoxue will be my personal assistant.

127
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,279
From now on, her opinions

128
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:54,759
will be my opinions.
